Student Record Management

Tasks:

Insert a student object (USN, name, sem, year_of_admission) to MongoDB.

Search students using a partial name match.

Skills: Node.js MongoDB driver, CRUD, regex

# Steps---

1. Initialize Node.js project.

2. Install packages:
  npm install express mongoose body-parser

3. Setup MongoDB connection using Mongoose.

4. Create schema for student.

5. Define two routes:
  POST to insert
  GET to search by partial name using regex
